name: Forge-Assisted Industry BP
desc: Contains the technological specifications and an industrial-grade nanoforge to allow for the construction and maintenance of this industry or structure.

name: Exo-Tech Blueprint Package
desc: Enables heavy industry to construct the more common ship hulls, weapons, and fighter LPCs from the "exo-tech" school of design. A doctrine focused on phase ships and their supporting lineup.

name: Warp Catalyst
desc:
A crystalline structure made out of an unknown material. It is in essence a heavily specialized accumulator, made to resist extreme loads of flux and deliver it towards its final destination.

The secret to this marvels method of construction was only known to few within the faction, it is unknown if any of them still remain within the sector.

name: Artifact
desc: An ancient artifact that can be integrated into a fleet to provide additional benefits. Only one can be active at a time. More information will be provided via the "Artifacts" intel tab (located in the "Personal" section) when integrating for the first time.
